WEBVTT

00:01.968 --> 00:03.526
<i>Previously on</i> One Tree Hill:

00:03.602 --> 00:06.265
I'm the one who did it.
I broke her windshield.

00:06.339 --> 00:08.899
When I got off the bus,
I saw Haley kissing some guy.

00:08.975 --> 00:12.934
He was kind of scrawny, had a guitar case,
sort of pelty hair.

00:20.520 --> 00:21.885
I took the test.

00:23.790 --> 00:25.781
We'll know in a couple of days.

00:27.027 --> 00:28.551
Thank you.

00:31.097 --> 00:32.997
I'm tired of running, Peyton.

00:33.900 --> 00:36.835
Come with me.
Let's bring Jenny back home.

00:38.071 --> 00:39.868
Something happened tonight.

00:40.540 --> 00:42.030
I asked her to marry me.

00:42.108 --> 00:44.975
You and I are the only ones
who know the truth about Jules.

00:45.045 --> 00:46.740
And I'm willing to keep it a secret.

00:46.813 --> 00:48.542
What do you want from me?

00:48.715 --> 00:50.876
I'm sure we can work something out.

